    "collapsible_content_EHD9fH": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_tab_CPXG4W": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does the Honiture G20 support vacuuming and mopping, and what is its maximum suction power?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes, the G20 is a <strong>3-in-1 sweeping, vacuuming, and mopping<\/strong> robot. It delivers a strong suction of <strong>4500Pa<\/strong> with 3 adjustable levels. With a 450ml dustbin and 250ml water tank, it handles both wet and dry messes simultaneously.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_U9jY8C": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What navigation technology does the G20 use, and how does it plan its route?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The G20 uses <strong>Gyroscope Navigation<\/strong> for smart routing. It mainly follows a <strong>Zigzag (Bow-shaped) cleaning path<\/strong>, which boosts cleaning efficiency up to 95%. It also supports Random, Spot, and Edge cleaning modes.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_BcjXbt": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does the G20 have special functions for carpets and what is its obstacle climbing ability?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes, the G20 features an <strong>Automatic Carpet Suction Boost<\/strong> to maximize power when a carpet is detected. It can easily overcome obstacles and thresholds up to a <strong>15° incline<\/strong>. Its slim design (<strong>76mm<\/strong>) allows it to clean effectively under furniture.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_4WLGwd": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is the maximum run time of the G20, and how are virtual boundaries set?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The G20 has a maximum run time of up to <strong>180 minutes<\/strong> thanks to its 2600mAh battery. Virtual boundaries (no-go zones) are set easily using <strong>magnetic strip virtual walls<\/strong> included with the device.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_qEgbxV": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I control the Honiture G20, and does it support voice commands?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The G20 offers multiple control options: <strong>App control<\/strong> (remote scheduling), <strong>remote control<\/strong>, physical buttons, and yes, <strong>voice control<\/strong> via smart assistants like Alexa. It also features automatic return-to-charge functionality.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        }
      },
